{"tid":2456271,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"咁樣係咪唔夠愛男朋友。。。","createTime":"2021-03-21T19:40:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T10:26:42.000Z","uid":345401,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e27859d60d712f3fb1e5bf5f435974df7e23a912","tid":2456271,"uid":345401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T19:40:48.000Z","msg":"同男朋友一齊兩年半<br />\n一向唔會管佢 <br />\n不論做咩 去邊 都唔會管<br />\n男朋友會自己報到行蹤<br />\n我又唔覺佢有出軌<br />\n以前見到佢like ex既相會嬲<br />\n但同佢講就好容易比佢成功遊花園當無事<br />\n<br />\n但最近發現自己好似唔會嬲佢咁<br />\n生日無要求要咩生日禮物 連蛋糕都無 但我唔會嬲<br />\n紀念品無特別做咩慶祝 無禮物 我又唔會嬲<br />\n同佢可以好耐唔見 我又唔嬲<br />\n有時候又覺得佢做咩都唔關我事<br />\n最近佢暗示想同我結婚 認定我係終身伴侶<br />\n但我開始有懷疑同驚 <br />\n<br />\n有人話唔嬲其實係因為唔夠愛<br />\n係咪真係咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55a7bed8b946905891e3d4ff45a9bc7784f0a241","tid":2456271,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T19:59:42.000Z","msg":"你根本唔愛佢"},{"pid":"76dc91175714ba3a0a574ea6fa9f7398f55c12e9","tid":2456271,"uid":303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T20:03:18.000Z","msg":"試下調轉 你做1佢做0"},{"pid":"27c514249dc44c6bf6355f4662c26a52cac08d35","tid":2456271,"uid":345401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76dc91175714ba3a0a574ea6fa9f7398f55c12e9","tid":2456271,"uid":303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T20:03:18.000Z","msg":"試下調轉 你做1佢做0"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T20:19:40.000Z","msg":"非gay post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ce51ddc055b514771537938fc650bca13611435","tid":2456271,"uid":345401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55a7bed8b946905891e3d4ff45a9bc7784f0a241","tid":2456271,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T19:59:42.000Z","msg":"你根本唔愛佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T20:20:09.000Z","ms